            . I am a Police-constable. I saw the prisoner in the custody of Mr. Clark; I received this<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183105120069"></xptr>bottle from Freeman - Mrs. Osborne was standing in the road at the time; I believe it contains port wine.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received an excellent character.</p>
